  "texts": [
    "This research question aims to investigate the potential impact of integrating Chat GPT-3 technology on student engagement, teacher workload, and instructional quality.",
    "By understanding the advantages and disadvantages of this technology in education, we can better assess its potential to improve the educational experience for students and teachers alike.",
    "Numerous reasons both in favor of and against the use of Chat GPT in education have been found in our literature review.",
    "Concerns have also been raised regarding Chat GPT's usage in the classroom.Our research indicates that although Chat GPT has a lot of promise as an educational tool, there are certain drawbacks and difficulties with it.",
    "These benefits and drawbacks should be carefully addressed before implementing Chat GPT in the classroom, with an emphasis on responsible use."
